{"tid":443960,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【中共十九大】教育部長：中國將成世界人們最想留學地方","createTime":"2017-10-22T05:56:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-27T00:43:46.000Z","uid":39464,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"5df9c14f9159bb076d75b55b8ddb68a896f764d3","tid":443960,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T05:56:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n 中共十九大中，各部門不僅報告過去年的豐功偉績，又預視未來的鴻圖大計，然而當中有幾多會成真，只能用時間去證門。教育部長陳寶生在今天上午的十九大新聞中心記者會上表示，2049年，中國教育將站立在世界中心，引領世界教育發展，中國的標準甚至成為世界的標準。<br />\n<br />\n陳寶生指出，屆時，中國將成為世界上人們最嚮往的留學目的地，將有各國願意和中華文化實現交流融合、學習交流中國發展經驗的有知識的學生、老師來中國交流，並在交流中實現共同進步。世界教育發展的規則，中國將有更大的發言權，並為世界教育提供中國方案、中國智慧，中國的教材、包括漢語拼音的教材也將走向世界。中國人民受教育的權利會得到全面維護，受教育的美好需求都可以保障。<br />\n<br />\n中國之聲 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20171022/57362573\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20171022%2F57362573&d=9JwYeKXHddSTeQeS7%2B%2BYkb%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=745c8f05\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20171022%2F57362573&h=948b7982\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20171022/57362573</a>"},{"pid":"30aed33720b59c0af4ce89196868453efeabe17d","tid":443960,"uid":62532,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T05:58:00.000Z","msg":"由領導做起啦好無"},{"pid":"3616f8a680ace490518b2f4d66125508439cb2c9","tid":443960,"uid":51129,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T06:00:54.000Z","msg":"潛台詞：班留學撚會俾我捉曬返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07a5b0fa2de1cfaf1d30e96d21ccefeb97cd6d3f","tid":443960,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T06:01